com.esri.mo2.cs.geod
Class PEFactory

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.esri.mo2.cs.geod.PEFactory
public class PEFactory
extends Object

PEFactory represents a means of creating coordinate systems from a specified string or id. The supported objects are coordinate systems (GCS, PCS) or datum transformations
